CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Nuveen Multi-Market Income Fund is a United States based closed-end management investment company. The Fund will invest primarily in debt securities, including, but not limited to, U.S. agency and privately issued mortgage-backed securities, corporate debt securities, and asset-backed securities. At least 65% of the Funds total assets must be invested in securities that, at the time of purchase, are rated investment-grade or of comparable quality.
